  <entry>
    <title>bochs-linux0-12-环境搭建</title>
    <link href="/myblog/2023/12/29/bochs-linux0-12-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/"/>
    <url>/myblog/2023/12/29/bochs-linux0-12-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>折腾了一个上午，终于搭建好 bochs 安装和 linux0.12环境搭建，所以想记录一下，避免以后忘记。</p><hr /><h1 id="环境">环境</h1><p>操作系统：Ubuntu 22.04 LST</p><p>bochs 版本：2.7</p><p>测试的linux版本：0.12（软盘启动）</p><p>参考书籍：《linux0.12完全注释》，赵炯</p><h1 id="流程">流程</h1><h2 id="安装-bochs">安装 bochs</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">sudo apt install bochs bochs-x<br><span class="hljs-comment"># bochs 是 IA-32 PC emulator</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># bochs-x 是 X11 plugin for Bochs, 因为 bochs 需要运行在 X11 桌面协议下</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="下载-linux-0.12系统软件包">下载 linux-0.12系统软件包</h2><p>赵炯老师书里给的链接是http://oldlinux.org/Linux.old/bochs/linux-0.12-080324.zip 。</p><p>下载并解压后文件夹结构如下：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-string">linux-0.12-080324</span><br><span class="hljs-string">├──</span> <span class="hljs-string">Bochs-2.3.6.exe</span><br><span class="hljs-string">├──</span> <span class="hljs-string">SYSTEM.MAP</span><br><span class="hljs-string">├──</span> <span class="hljs-string">bochs-2.3.6-1.i586.rpm</span><br><span class="hljs-string">├──</span> <span class="hljs-string">bochsout.txt</span><br><span class="hljs-string">├──</span> <span class="hljs-string">bochsrc-0.12-fd.bxrc</span><br><span class="hljs-string">├──</span> <span class="hljs-string">bochsrc-0.12-hd.bxrc</span><br><span class="hljs-string">├──</span> <span class="hljs-string">bochsrc-sample.txt</span><br><span class="hljs-string">├──</span> <span class="hljs-string">bootimage-0.12-fd</span><br><span class="hljs-string">├──</span> <span class="hljs-string">bootimage-0.12-hd</span><br><span class="hljs-string">├──</span> <span class="hljs-string">debug.bat</span><br><span class="hljs-string">├──</span> <span class="hljs-string">diska.img</span><br><span class="hljs-string">├──</span> <span class="hljs-string">diskb.img</span><br><span class="hljs-string">├──</span> <span class="hljs-string">linux-0.12-README</span><br><span class="hljs-string">├──</span> <span class="hljs-string">rootimage-0.12-fd</span><br><span class="hljs-string">└──</span> <span class="hljs-string">rootimage-0.12-hd</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>我这里需要用到的是</p><ul><li>bochsrc-0.12-fd.bxrc ，软盘启动的配置文件</li><li>bootimage-0.12-fd ，启动映像</li><li>rootimage-0.12-fd ，根文件映像</li><li>bochsout.txt ，debug的输出文件</li></ul><h2 id="运行-linux0.12">运行 linux0.12</h2><p>运行命令：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">bochs -f bochsrc-0.12-fd.bxrc<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>实际情况下，当运行这句命令后，会出现若干问题，我这里展示我所所遇到的。</p><h3 id="常见问题">常见问题</h3><p>（1）<strong>directive 'vga_update_interval' notunderstood</strong>：原因：Bochs版本过新，不兼容一些旧选项，将.bxrc中的vga_update_interval删除掉</p><p>（2）<strong>Bochs黑屏</strong>： 在终端输入c</p><img src="/myblog/2023/12/29/bochs-linux0-12-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/image-20231229162258808.png" class="" title="image-20231229162258808"><p>（3）<strong>bx_dbg_read_linear: physical memory readerror</strong>： a) 将bochsrc文件中第10行vgaromimage:/usr/share/vgabios/vgabios.bin改为 vgaromimage:file=/usr/share/vgabios/vgabios.bin 或 vgaromimage:file=/usr/share/bochs/VGABIOS-lgpl-latest b) 从https://github.com/bochs-emu/Bochs/raw/REL_2_7_FINAL/bochs/bios/BIOS-bochs-latest下载该文件，修改 romimage: file=该文件路径，或者将位于<code>/usr/share/bochs/</code> 下的 <code>BIOS-bochs-latest</code>替换成 该文件。</p><p>（4）<strong>看到insert root floppy and press ENTER</strong>：解决：https://www.cnblogs.com/raina/p/13212177.html 点击右上角的config,会出现"Bochs Runtime Options"； 然后更改floppy disk0的名字为同目录下的rootimage-0.12-fd，不断继续回车，这时软件会自动识别；重新出现"Bochs Runtime Options"后选择"Continue simulation"</p><img src="/myblog/2023/12/29/bochs-linux0-12-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/image-20231229162314479.png" class="" title="image-20231229162314479"><img src="/myblog/2023/12/29/bochs-linux0-12-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/image-20231229162329510.png" class="" title="image-20231229162329510"><img src="/myblog/2023/12/29/bochs-linux0-12-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/image-20231229162342379.png" class="" title="image-20231229162342379"><p>（5）<strong>timeout! no client present</strong>：安装bochs-x，命令为 sudo apt install bochs-x</p>]]></content>
    
    
