    <title>Centos7 安装PyTorch和GPU环境支持</title>
    <link href="/myblog/2023/10/19/Centos7-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85PyTorch%E5%92%8CGPU%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81/"/>
    <url>/myblog/2023/10/19/Centos7-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85PyTorch%E5%92%8CGPU%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<hr /><blockquote><p>后来发现PyTorch包里已经集成有CUDA和cudnn。。。可以不用安装cuda、cudnn。</p><p>第一次失败，很正常，最好可以照个快照保存一下状态，方便回滚。</p><p>系统：Centos 7</p><p>显卡：GRID A100</p><p>PyTorch版本：2.1.0</p><p>CUDA版本：12.1.1</p><p>cuDNN版本：8.9.3</p><p>驱动版本：535.104.12</p></blockquote><h2id="pytorchcudacudnnnvidia驱动之间的兼容性">Pytorch、CUDA、cudnn、NVIDIA驱动之间的兼容性</h2><p>首先，可以明确，<strong>CUDA(CUDAToolkit)、PyTorch、cudnn之间有一定的匹配关系</strong>，不能随便安装。</p><h3 id="cuda与驱动">CUDA与驱动</h3><p>从<ahref="https://docs.nvidia.com/cuda/cuda-toolkit-release-notes/index.html">CUDA官网</a>可以看到，<strong>CUDA与驱动的兼容性</strong>如下：</p><img src="/myblog/2023/10/19/Centos7-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85PyTorch%E5%92%8CGPU%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81/image-20231022212452719.png" class="" title="image-20231022212452719"><p>值得注意的是，在CUDAToolkit的安装程序中附加了NVIDIA驱动的安装，但是官方并不建议，官方建议到<ahref="https://www.nvidia.com/drivers">NVIDIA驱动选择界面</a>根据自己的TeslaGPU来选择驱动。</p><p>也就是说，NVIDIA驱动的版本是越新越好。</p><blockquote><p>另外，可以在<ahref="https://developer.nvidia.cn/cuda-gpus">这里</a>查看自己显卡的算力。这是<ahref="https://www.nvidia.com/en-us/data-center/a100/">A100显卡</a>的。</p><p>关于CUDA向后兼容性的理解，可以看看<ahref="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/459431437">这篇文章</a>。</p></blockquote><h3 id="cudnn与cuda">cudnn与CUDA</h3><p><strong>cuDNN</strong>是用于深度神经网络的GPU加速库，相当于是对CUDA的补充。可以在<ahref="https://developer.nvidia.com/rdp/cudnn-download">cuDNN官网</a>选择与已安装的CUDA版本对应的下载。</p><blockquote><p>值得注意的是，tensorflow-gpu对cuDNN的版本也有一定限制，可以在<ahref="https://tensorflow.google.cn/install/source#tested_build_configurations">这里</a>查看。就是不知道PyTorch有没有？！在<ahref="https://pytorch.org/get-started/locally/#linux-prerequisites">这里</a>可以看到CUDA只要满足PyTorch要求的最低版本即可，越新越好。</p><p>To install PyTorch via Anaconda, and you do have a CUDA-capablesystem, in the above selector, choose OS: Linux, Package: Conda and theCUDA version suited to your machine. Often, the latest CUDA version isbetter. Then, run the command that is presented to you.</p></blockquote><h3 id="pytorch与cudapython">PyTorch与CUDA、Python</h3><p>在<ahref="https://pytorch.org/">PyTorch</a>官网上，可以看到Pytorch对于不同版本的CUDA有不同的安装指令。</p><img src="/myblog/2023/10/19/Centos7-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85PyTorch%E5%92%8CGPU%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81/image-20231019144337409.png" class="" title="image-20231019144337409"><p>在<ahref="https://pytorch.org/get-started/locally/">PyTorch的get-started界面</a>可以看到PyTorch对OS发行版、Python版本($$3.8)都有一定要求，也有验证是否能使用GPU的方法。</p><p>总结，<strong>不同版本的PyTorch要求不同的最低版本的CUDA和不同版本的Python，而CUDA又决定该选择什么版本的cuDNN</strong>。</p><h2 id="准备工作">准备工作</h2><h3 id="禁用nouveau">禁用nouveau</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 法1</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 查看系统自带的驱动：</span><br>lsmod | grep nouveau<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 编辑如下文件：</span><br>sudo vi /usr/lib/modprobe.d/dist-blacklist.conf<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 然后在最后添加如下内容：</span><br>blacklist nouveau<br>options nouveau modeset=0<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 法2</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 有的路径是/etc/modprobe.d/blacklist.conf</span><br>sudo vi /usr/lib/modprobe.d/blacklist-nouveau.conf<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 然后在最后添加如下内容：</span><br>blacklist nouveau<br>options nouveau modeset=0<br>sudo modprobe -r nouveau<br>reboot<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 法3 成功</span><br>lsmod | grep nouveau<br>sudo vi /etc/modprobe.d/blacklist-nouveau.conf<br>sudo dracut --force<br>reboot<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="查看是否有显卡">查看是否有显卡</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">lspci | grep VGA<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 返回</span><br>00:02.0 VGA compatible controller: Red Hat, Inc. QXL paravirtual graphic card (rev 04)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="查看显卡型号">查看显卡型号</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">lspci | grep NVIDIA<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 返回</span><br>00:05.0 3D controller: NVIDIA Corporation GA100 [GRID A100 PCIe 40GB] (rev a1)<br>00:06.0 3D controller: NVIDIA Corporation GA100 [GRID A100 PCIe 40GB] (rev a1)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="查看cuda是否安装">查看cuda是否安装</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">nvcc -V<br><span class="hljs-built_in">ls</span> /usr/local | grep cuda<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="查看驱动是否安装">查看驱动是否安装</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">nvidia-smi<br><span class="hljs-built_in">ls</span> /proc/driver | grep nvidia<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="检查os发行版是否支持">检查OS发行版是否支持</h3><img src="/myblog/2023/10/19/Centos7-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85PyTorch%E5%92%8CGPU%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81/image-20231019144543610.png" class="" title="image-20231019144543610"><p>检查链接：<ahref="https://pytorch.org/get-started/locally/#supported-linux-distributions">这里</a></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 查看内核和发行版</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">uname</span> -a &amp;&amp; <span class="hljs-built_in">cat</span> /etc/redhat-release<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 返回</span><br>Linux n1 3.10.0-1160.99.1.el7.x86_64 <span class="hljs-comment">#1 SMP Wed Sep 13 14:19:20 UTC 2023 x86_64 x86_64 x86_64 GNU/Linux</span><br>CentOS Linux release 7.9.2009 (Core)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="检查python版本">检查Python版本</h3><p>Python 3.8 or greater。</p><h2 id="下载并安装好相应程序文件">下载并安装好相应程序文件</h2><h3 id="nvidia驱动">NVIDIA驱动</h3><p><strong>驱动越新越好</strong>。</p><p><strong>安装基础rpm依赖包</strong>：安装Nvidia驱动所需要的依赖包为kernel-devel、gcc、dkms。验证cudn，编译并运行验证Sample代码所需要的依赖包为gcc-c++。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 验证当前服务器内核版本是否与yum提供的kernel-devel版本是否一致</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">uname</span> -r &amp;&amp; yum list | grep kernel-devel<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 不一致,更换内核版本</span><br>sudo yum install kernel-devel-$(<span class="hljs-built_in">uname</span> -r)<br><br>sudo yum install gcc dkms<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><ahref="https://www.nvidia.com/download/index.aspx?lang=en-us">选择界面</a>，我选择</p><img src="/myblog/2023/10/19/Centos7-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85PyTorch%E5%92%8CGPU%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81/image-20231019104829833.png" class="" title="image-20231019104829833"><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">wget https://us.download.nvidia.cn/tesla/535.104.12/NVIDIA-Linux-x86_64-535.104.12.run<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装过程中允许DMKS。</p><img src="/myblog/2023/10/19/Centos7-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85PyTorch%E5%92%8CGPU%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81/image-20231019120541034.png" class="" title="image-20231019120541034"><img src="/myblog/2023/10/19/Centos7-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85PyTorch%E5%92%8CGPU%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81/image-20231019120651413.png" class="" title="image-20231019120651413"><p>选择No。</p><img src="/myblog/2023/10/19/Centos7-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85PyTorch%E5%92%8CGPU%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81/image-20231019120759902.png" class="" title="image-20231019120759902"><img src="/myblog/2023/10/19/Centos7-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85PyTorch%E5%92%8CGPU%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81/image-20231019120904173.png" class="" title="image-20231019120904173"><p>选择Yes。</p><p><strong>验证</strong>：</p><img src="/myblog/2023/10/19/Centos7-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85PyTorch%E5%92%8CGPU%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81/image-20231019121055481.png" class="" title="image-20231019121055481"><h3 id="cuda">CUDA</h3><p><a href="https://developer.nvidia.com/cuda-toolkit-archive">CUDAToolkit 选择界面</a>，我选择<ahref="https://developer.nvidia.com/cuda-12-1-1-download-archive?target_os=Linux&amp;target_arch=x86_64&amp;Distribution=CentOS&amp;target_version=7&amp;target_type=runfile_local">CUDA12.1.1</a>。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">wget https://developer.download.nvidia.com/compute/cuda/12.1.1/local_installers/cuda_12.1.1_530.30.02_linux.run<br>sudo sh cuda_12.1.1_530.30.02_linux.run<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装过程中注意，取消driver的选择，安装好之后</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">vi ~/.bashrc<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 最后加入</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">export</span> CUDA_HOME=/usr/local/cuda<br><span class="hljs-built_in">export</span> LD_LIBRARY_PATH=<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;CUDA_HOME&#125;</span>/lib64<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;LD_LIBRARY_PATH+:<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;LD_LIBRARY_PATH&#125;</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">export</span> PATH=<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;CUDA_HOME&#125;</span>/bin:<span class="hljs-variable">$PATH</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 执行</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">source</span> ~/.bashrc<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 验证</span><br>nvcc -V<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="/myblog/2023/10/19/Centos7-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85PyTorch%E5%92%8CGPU%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81/image-20231019121357145.png" class="" title="image-20231019121357145"><img src="/myblog/2023/10/19/Centos7-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85PyTorch%E5%92%8CGPU%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81/image-20231019122624939.png" class="" title="image-20231019122624939"><p>没用的用space键或Enter取消。</p><p>完成后：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">===========<br>= Summary =<br>===========<br><br>Driver:   Not Selected<br>Toolkit:  Installed <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> /usr/local/cuda-12.1/<br><br>Please make sure that<br> -   PATH includes /usr/local/cuda-12.1/bin<br> -   LD_LIBRARY_PATH includes /usr/local/cuda-12.1/lib64, or, add /usr/local/cuda-12.1/lib64 to /etc/ld.so.conf and run ldconfig as root<br><br>To uninstall the CUDA Toolkit, run cuda-uninstaller <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> /usr/local/cuda-12.1/bin<br>***WARNING: Incomplete installation! This installation did not install the CUDA Driver. A driver of version at least 530.00 is required <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> CUDA 12.1 functionality to work.<br>To install the driver using this installer, run the following <span class="hljs-built_in">command</span>, replacing &lt;CudaInstaller&gt; with the name of this run file:<br>    sudo &lt;CudaInstaller&gt;.run --silent --driver<br><br>Logfile is /var/log/cuda-installer.log<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="cudnn">cudnn</h3><p>可以在<ahref="https://developer.nvidia.com/rdp/cudnn-archive">这里</a>挑选。我选择<ahref="https://developer.nvidia.com/rdp/cudnn-archive#a-collapse893-120">DownloadcuDNN v8.9.3 (July 11th, 2023), for CUDA 12.x</a>。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 链接过长，所以使用-O参数和双引号修饰符，发现tm的下载的竟然是网页？？可能链接有时效性</span><br>wget -O cudnn-linux-x86_64-8.9.3.28_cuda12-archive.tar.xz <span class="hljs-string">&quot;https://developer.download.nvidia.cn/compute/cudnn/secure/8.9.3/local_installers/12.x/cudnn-linux-x86_64-8.9.3.28_cuda12-archive.tar.xz?HMC_802VfF0fBq1s9Rj92E7-S3swVruOO85p_xb0yhmFzp78Ee3OCWG-3AyVJp3M_HUllCiwyddhAkw-LSOwQlvt1SSOvUipIyeXSr1pQDokwKjWAyVMqBu8nVf65zrZAAH1Sd6MvndL2WdKEglsu5OW5PRKnRe7atBz9rDCEqCO3rQzOVwDAvJ3XCySNv864H1kOJOd4aVYbWI0HbQ6QY4=&amp;t=eyJscyI6InJlZiIsImxzZCI6IlJFRi1kb2NzLm52aWRpYS5jb20vIn0=&quot;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 直接到直链下载 https://developer.download.nvidia.com/compute/redist/cudnn</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 但是直链仅支持v8.8</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 法1：去https://developer.nvidia.com/rdp/cudnn-archive获取直链,在其失效之前赶紧下载</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 也可以用scp传输</span><br>scp -P 端口 ./本机某文件 用户名@远程主机名:远程主机某目录<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装过程：https://docs.nvidia.com/deeplearning/cudnn/install-guide/index.html#installlinux-tar</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">tar -xvf cudnn-linux-<span class="hljs-variable">$arch</span>-8.x.x.x_cudaX.Y-archive.tar.xz<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 安装</span><br>sudo <span class="hljs-built_in">cp</span> cudnn-*-archive/include/cudnn*.h /usr/local/cuda/include <br>sudo <span class="hljs-built_in">cp</span> -P cudnn-*-archive/lib/libcudnn* /usr/local/cuda/lib64 <br>sudo <span class="hljs-built_in">chmod</span> a+r /usr/local/cuda/include/cudnn*.h /usr/local/cuda/lib64/libcudnn*<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="pytorch">PyTorch</h3><p><a href="https://pytorch.org/">PyTorch</a>官网</p><img src="/myblog/2023/10/19/Centos7-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85PyTorch%E5%92%8CGPU%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81/image-20231019103233883.png" class="" title="image-20231019103233883"><blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># conda</span><br>conda create -n <span class="hljs-built_in">test</span> python=3.9<br>conda install pytorch torchvision torchaudio pytorch-cuda=12.1 -c pytorch -c nvidia<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># pip</span><br>pip3 install torch torchvision torchaudio<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><h2 id="验证">验证</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> torch<br>x = torch.rand(<span class="hljs-number">5</span>, <span class="hljs-number">3</span>)<br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(x)<br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;cuda是否可用: &quot;</span>,torch.cuda.is_available())<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 输出应该是</span><br>tensor([[<span class="hljs-number">0.3380</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0.3845</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0.3217</span>],<br>        [<span class="hljs-number">0.8337</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0.9050</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0.2650</span>],<br>        [<span class="hljs-number">0.2979</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0.7141</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0.9069</span>],<br>        [<span class="hljs-number">0.1449</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0.1132</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0.1375</span>],<br>        [<span class="hljs-number">0.4675</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0.3947</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0.1426</span>]])<br>true<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="更新一下">更新一下</h2><p><strong>因为pytorch自带cuda和cudnn</strong>，你只需要准备支持高于这个cuda版本的显卡驱动就可以了。（不过这个cuda只包含给pytorch用的库函数，不包括cudatoolchain，比如nvcc等等，如果需要完整的cuda还是要自己装）。。。。。</p><p>进入pytorch的安装目录就可以看到，pytorch在编译的时候已经把cuda的库静态链接到了自己的库里，用conda或者pip安装的包已经打包好这些了。</p><p>test环境里的包：</p><img src="/myblog/2023/10/19/Centos7-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85PyTorch%E5%92%8CGPU%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81/image-20231019140049763.png" class="" title="image-20231019140049763"><p>nvidia文件夹里：</p><img src="/myblog/2023/10/19/Centos7-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85PyTorch%E5%92%8CGPU%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81/image-20231019140141359.png" class="" title="image-20231019140141359"><p>torch的lib目录：</p><img src="/myblog/2023/10/19/Centos7-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85PyTorch%E5%92%8CGPU%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81/image-20231019140342840.png" class="" title="image-20231019140342840"><p>链接：https://blog.csdn.net/qq_36944952/article/details/109460760</p><h2 id="工具">工具</h2><h3 id="清理">清理</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 包含了GUI，所以不喜欢</span><br>sudo yum install bleachbit-cli<br>bleachbit --list  <span class="hljs-comment"># 列出可用的清理项目和应用程序选项</span><br>bleachbit --clean system.cache system.tmp <span class="hljs-comment"># 例如</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 原生命令</span><br>sudo yum clean all  <span class="hljs-comment"># 清除缓存的yum包</span><br>sudo journalctl --vacuum-time=3d  <span class="hljs-comment"># 清除日志</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># conda清理</span><br>conda clean -p<br>conda clean -t<br>conda clean -y -a<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># pip清理</span><br>pip cache purge<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
